SELECT [p].[Id] AS [ProductId], [c].[Id] AS [CategoryId], [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [c].[Name] AS [CategoryName], [p].[ImageUrl]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
WHERE [p].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit) AND [p].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit) AND [p].[ShopId] = @__shopId_0 AND [p].[Stock] > 0
